sequenceDiagram
    participant M as Main
    participant G as Game
    participant S as Snake
    participant F as Food
    participant GS as GameScreen

    M->>G: start game
    G->>S: move snake
    G->>F: generate food
    GS->>GS: draw snake
    GS->>GS: draw food
    GS->>GS: draw score
    S->>S: change direction
    S->>S: move
    S->>S: eat food
    S->>S: collide with wall?
    S->>S: collide with self?
    G-->>GS: draw snake
    G-->>GS: draw food
    G-->>GS: draw score
    G-->>GS: draw game over
    M->>G: end game
